     							 <div class="card-body">
       								 <p>The current project specifically works on social sustainability, aiming to improve individual well-being in the societies. Detailed information can be found in a following paragraph. </p>
									 <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#ToC">Take me there >></a>
     							 </div>
